pt-ui-mods (1.0.20180508-1) stretch; urgency=medium

  * Added Bluetooth to lxpanel
  * Fixed 'need 2 terminal button keypresses' bug
  * rpi port: Install qtc5t configuration file to theme Qt applications
  * rpi port: Use pi-topFONTLt instead of pi-topFONT Light for applications which ignore font weight
  * rpi port: Use rc_gui and /etc/default/keyboard instead of lxkeymap to manage key layouts

